The paper deals with computational biology problems related to trees, and involves complexity analysis and approximation algorithms. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-categories of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Game Theory (cs.GT). Among these, cs.DM and cs.CC are the most likely categories, as the paper involves combinatorial and algorithmic aspects of tree problems.
